# Model config: Qwen3.6-27B (Q6_K, dense, thinking model)
#
# Rationale:
#   - Qwen3 thinking-mode sampling: temp 0.6, top-p 0.95, top-k 20, min-p 0.
#     (Do NOT use greedy/temp 0 — Qwen3 degrades and can loop in thinking mode.)
#   - --presence-penalty 1.0 curbs occasional repetition on long generations.
#   - q8_0 KV cache (launcher default) is a good quality/VRAM trade for a dense 27B.

: "${MODEL:=Qwen3.6-27B/Qwen3.6-27B-Q6_K.gguf}"

LLAMA_ARGS+=(--temp 0.6 --top-p 0.95 --top-k 20 --min-p 0 --presence-penalty 1.0)
